eu.cqse.check.framework.util

Class TypeNameTokenCollection

  • java.lang.Object
    • eu.cqse.check.framework.util.TypeNameTokenCollection

  • public class TypeNameTokenCollection
extends java.lang.Object
    A collection that manages tokens of a type name. It distinguishes between primitive and non-primitive types and formats the type name accordingly.
